In the command line:
```
java -jar target\downstream-data-factory-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar -Dloader.main=com.xxx.globalpayments.feeds.downstream.DownstreamDataFactoryApplication org.springframework.boot.loader.PropertiesLauncher
